description:
Rapper Dreamdoll joins the ladies of Lip Service this week and opens up about her relationship with her father while hes in jail, getting plastic surgery for the wrong reasons, and much more! The ladies address their early experiences with oral sex...and even the time Dreamdoll threw up on the dick! You think red snapper tastes better the second time? Enjoy!
